import * as Clipboard from 'expo-clipboard';
import React, { useEffect, useState } from "react";
import { RefreshControl, Alert, View, Text } from 'react-native';
import { Container, DataContent, DataLab, DataReplyLab, DataLimiter, Copy, CopyLab,  Copied, CopiedLab } from "./styles/show";

const ShowPreco = ({ route, navigation }) => { 

  return (
  <Container>
    <DataLimiter>    
      <DataLab> Código: <DataReplyLab onPress={async () => await Clipboard.setString(route.params.cod) }> {route.params.cod} </DataReplyLab> </DataLab>
      <DataLab> Produto: <DataReplyLab onPress={async () => await Clipboard.setString(route.params.produto) }> {route.params.produto} </DataReplyLab> </DataLab>
      <DataLab> CodGrupo: <DataReplyLab onPress={async () => await Clipboard.setString(route.params.codgrupo) }> {route.params.codgrupo} </DataReplyLab> </DataLab>
      <DataLab> CodSubgrupo: <DataReplyLab onPress={async () => await Clipboard.setString(route.params.codsubgrupo) }> {route.params.codsubgrupo} </DataReplyLab> </DataLab>
      <DataLab> CodFornecedor: <DataReplyLab onPress={async () => await Clipboard.setString(route.params.codfornecedor) }> {route.params.codfornecedor} </DataReplyLab> </DataLab>
      <DataLab> CodMarca: <DataReplyLab onPress={async () => await Clipboard.setString(route.params.codmarca) }> {route.params.codmarca} </DataReplyLab> </DataLab>
      <DataLab> Data da Ultima Compra: <DataReplyLab onPress={async () => await Clipboard.setString(route.params.data_ultimacompra) }> {route.params.data_ultimacompra} </DataReplyLab> </DataLab>
      <DataLab> Preço de Custo: <DataReplyLab onPress={async () => await Clipboard.setString(route.params.precocusto) }> {route.params.precocusto} </DataReplyLab> </DataLab>
      <DataLab> Preço de Venda: <DataReplyLab onPress={async () => await Clipboard.setString(route.params.precovenda) }> {route.params.precovenda} </DataReplyLab> </DataLab>
      <DataLab> Data da Ultima Venda: <DataReplyLab onPress={async () => await Clipboard.setString(route.params.data_ultimavenda) }> {route.params.data_ultimavenda} </DataReplyLab> </DataLab>           
      <DataLab> Aplicação: <DataReplyLab onPress={async () => await Clipboard.setString(route.params.aplicacao) }> {route.params.aplicacao} </DataReplyLab> </DataLab>           
      <DataLab> Localização: <DataReplyLab onPress={async () => await Clipboard.setString(route.params.localicazao) }> {route.params.localicazao} </DataReplyLab> </DataLab>           
      <DataLab> Foto: <DataReplyLab onPress={async () => await Clipboard.setString(route.params.foto) }> {route.params.foto} </DataReplyLab> </DataLab>           
      <DataLab> CST: <DataReplyLab onPress={async () => await Clipboard.setString(route.params.cst) }> {route.params.cst} </DataReplyLab> </DataLab>           
      <DataLab> Classificacao Fiscal: <DataReplyLab onPress={async () => await Clipboard.setString(route.params.classificacao_fiscal) }> {route.params.classificacao_fiscal} </DataReplyLab> </DataLab>
      <DataLab> Aliquota: <DataReplyLab onPress={async () => await Clipboard.setString(route.params.aliquota) }> {route.params.aliquota} </DataReplyLab> </DataLab>
      <DataLab> Situação: <DataReplyLab onPress={async () => await Clipboard.setString(route.params.situacao) }> {route.params.situacao} </DataReplyLab> </DataLab>          
      <DataLab> Preco Venda(1): <DataReplyLab onPress={async () => await Clipboard.setString(route.params.precovenda1) }> {route.params.precovenda1} </DataReplyLab> </DataLab>
      <DataLab> Preco Venda(2): <DataReplyLab onPress={async () => await Clipboard.setString(route.params.precovenda2) }> {route.params.precovenda2} </DataReplyLab> </DataLab>
      <DataLab> Referencia Fornecedor: <DataReplyLab onPress={async () => await Clipboard.setString(route.params.referencia_fornecedor) }> {route.params.referencia_fornecedor} </DataReplyLab> </DataLab>
      <DataLab> Csosn: <DataReplyLab onPress={async () => await Clipboard.setString(route.params.csosn) }> {route.params.csosn} </DataReplyLab> </DataLab>          
      <DataLab> Cest: <DataReplyLab onPress={async () => await Clipboard.setString(route.params.cest) }> {route.params.cest} </DataReplyLab> </DataLab>           
      <DataLab> Ind_cfop_nfce: <DataReplyLab onPress={async () => await Clipboard.setString(route.params.ind_cfop_nfce) }> {route.params.ind_cfop_nfce} </DataReplyLab> </DataLab>         
      <DataLab> CodBarra: <DataReplyLab onPress={async () => await Clipboard.setString(route.params.codbarra) }> {route.params.codbarra} </DataReplyLab> </DataLab>
      <DataLab> Unidade: <DataReplyLab onPress={async () => await Clipboard.setString(route.params.unidade) }> {route.params.unidade} </DataReplyLab> </DataLab>
      <DataLab> Ecommerce: <DataReplyLab onPress={async () => await Clipboard.setString(route.params.ecommerce) }> {route.params.ecommerce} </DataReplyLab> </DataLab>
      </DataLimiter>
      <Copy onPress={async () => await Clipboard.setString(
        		'Código : ' + route.params.cod + 
            '\n\nProduto : ' + route.params.nome + 
            '\n\nCodGrupo : ' + route.params.apelido + 
            '\n\nCodSubgrupo : ' + route.params.numero +
            '\n\nCodFornecedor : ' + route.params.endereco + 
            '\n\nCodMarca : ' + route.params.bairro + 
            '\n\nData da Ultima Compra : ' + route.params.cidade + 
            '\n\nPreço de Custo : ' + route.params.uf +
            '\n\nPreço de Venda : ' + route.params.cep +  
            '\n\nData da Ultima Venda : ' + route.params.complemento + 
            '\n\nAplicação : ' + route.params.telefone1 + 
            '\n\nLocalização : ' + route.params.telefone2 +
            '\n\nFoto : ' + route.params.telefone3 +  
            '\n\nCST : ' + route.params.celular + 
            '\n\nClassificacao Fiscal : ' + route.params.email + 
            '\n\nAliquota : ' + route.params.rg +
            '\n\nSituação : ' + route.params.cpf +
            '\n\nPreco Venda(1) : ' + route.params.data_cadastro + 
            '\n\nPreco Venda(2) : ' + route.params.obs1 + route.params.obs2 + route.params.obs3 + route.params.obs4 + route.params.obs5 + route.params.obs6 +
            '\n\nReferencia Fornecedor : ' + route.params.consumidor_final +		
            '\n\nCsosn : ' + route.params.consumidor_final +	
            '\n\nCest : ' + route.params.consumidor_final +		
            '\n\nInd_cfop_nfce : ' + route.params.consumidor_final +	
            '\n\nCodBarra : ' + route.params.consumidor_final +		
            '\n\nUnidade : ' + route.params.atb + 
            '\n\nEcommerce : ' + route.params.atb) }>
      <CopyLab> Copiar </CopyLab>
      </Copy>
  </Container>
  )

}

export default ShowPreco;
